13 April 2018 Technical media briefing on the Preparations for the funeral of the Late Mrs Winnie Madikizela-Mandela Members of the media are advised to attend a technical briefing ahead of the funeral service and burial of the late Mrs Winnie Madikizela-Mandela. The briefing will address logistical issues pertaining to the broadcast, camera positions, media transportation, parking, access to the funeral venue, etc.  This is to ensure a smooth operation on the day of the funeral. The details of the briefing are as follows:Date: Friday, 13  April 2018Time: 10h00Venue: Orlando Stadium, Ground floor Auditorium. Mrs Madikizela-Mandela will be buried on Saturday, 14 April 2018 at Orlando Stadium in Soweto followed by a burial at Fourways Memorial Park cemetery. For further details contact:  Ireen MagwaiCell: 082 440 5676 Pheliswa SebatiCell: 082 413 4609 Tshegofatso ModubuCell: 083 276 0786 Issued by Government Communication and Information System  